The '''2013 Swiss Indoors''' was a [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Tennis court#Indoor courts|indoor hard courts]]. It was the 44th edition of the event known as the [[Swiss Indoors]], and part of the [[ATP World Tour 500 series|500 series]] of the [[2013 ATP World Tour]]. It was held at the [[St. Jakobshalle]] in [[Basel]], [[Switzerland]], from October 21 through October 27, 2013. 

