===Other entrants===
The following players received wildcards into the singles main draw:
* {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Marco Chiudinelli]]
* {{flagicon|UKR}} [[Alexandr Dolgopolov]]
* {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Henri Laaksonen]] 

The following players received entry from the qualifying draw:
* {{flagicon|GER}} [[Benjamin Becker]] 
* {{flagicon|GER}} [[Tobias Kamke]] 
* {{flagicon|USA}} [[Denis Kudla]]
* {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Paul-Henri Mathieu]]

===Withdrawals===
* {{flagicon|USA}} [[Brian Baker (tennis)|Brian Baker]]
* {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Nikolay Davydenko]]
* {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Federico Delbonis]] (personal reasons)
* {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Marinko Matosevic]]
* {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Rafael Nadal]] (fatigue)
* {{flagicon|CAN}} [[Milos Raonic]] (personal reasons)

===Retirements===
* {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Carlos Berlocq]] (right foot pain)

