==Champions==
===Singles===
{{main|2013 Swiss Indoors – Singles}}
*{{flagicon|ARG}} '''[[Juan Martín del Potro]]''' defeated {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Roger Federer]], 7–6<sup>(7–3)</sup>, 2–6, 6–4

===Doubles===
{{main|2013 Swiss Indoors – Doubles}}
* {{flagicon|PHI}} '''[[Treat Huey]]''' / {{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Dominic Inglot]]''' defeated {{flagicon|AUT}} [[Julian Knowle]] / {{flagicon|AUT}} [[Oliver Marach]], 6–3, 3–6, [10–4]

